S.FORM: Tsai Ing-wen I 1956 a miheca saka 8 a folad saka 31 a romi'ad－ saka ci Tsai Ing-wen, malamikomoday a tamdaw. O Sawara'an no kitakit no Taiwan anini i ci Tsai Ing-wen, patirengan a romi'ad i 2016 a miheca saka 5 folad saka 20 a romi'ad.
